Step 1 - Introduction 1

Introduction

Note: Sample was done with the name Alumni workspace

1. A new workspace can be created with Power BI Admin Account, this will help:

- to have specific location/ a new folder to publish the Power BI report

- to share with the user from a specified location/ folder created

2. Add user & give access 

            - to read

            - to build

            - to share
